29
00:02:38,358 --> 00:02:40,961
‐ Yeah, they don't give you
much to start with.

30
00:02:41,027 --> 00:02:44,130
Don't worry, though. I can
transfer some funds to you.

31
00:02:44,197 --> 00:02:45,799
‐ Don't spend it on me here.

32
00:02:45,866 --> 00:02:49,269
Save it for when I come down to
Tokyo for Elza's next concert.

33
00:02:49,335 --> 00:02:50,737
Remember how you said
you'd take me

34
00:02:50,804 --> 00:02:53,073
to some expensive
sushi place after?

35
00:02:53,139 --> 00:02:54,675
‐ Hey, I never said that!

36
00:02:54,741 --> 00:02:56,342
‐ Busted!

37
00:02:56,409 --> 00:02:58,011
‐ Well, maybe if we win‐‐

38
00:02:58,078 --> 00:03:00,313
‐ I totally heard that!
You can't take it back.

39
00:03:00,380 --> 00:03:02,315
I'll remember what you said.

40
00:03:02,382 --> 00:03:04,250
‐ You need a gun, Miyu.

41
00:03:04,317 --> 00:03:05,952
Sorry. I mean Fukaziroh.

42
00:03:06,019 --> 00:03:09,089
Wait. Isn't Fukaziroh
what you called your dog?

43
00:03:09,155 --> 00:03:12,125
Why'd you name him that?

44
00:03:12,192 --> 00:03:13,627
‐ [barks]
‐ Fukaziroh: I wanted a dog

45
00:03:13,694 --> 00:03:15,662
for a first pet,
but my folks said nope,

46
00:03:15,729 --> 00:03:18,565
so I got a sparrow instead
and called him Tarou Shinohara,

47
00:03:18,632 --> 00:03:20,300
and when I finally got a dog

48
00:03:20,366 --> 00:03:21,935
I called him Fuka Jirou.
Clever, huh!

49
00:03:22,002 --> 00:03:27,340
[sighs] Poor ol' Fukaziroh.
Rest in peace, little fur ball.

50
00:03:27,407 --> 00:03:30,711
Amen. But you still
need money to buy a gun.

51
00:03:30,777 --> 00:03:32,613
‐ Oh, no worries.
Just talk to the guy

52
00:03:32,679 --> 00:03:34,314
who asked you
to sign up for this.

53
00:03:34,380 --> 00:03:37,250
‐ I could ask Goushi. Eh?

54
00:03:37,317 --> 00:03:38,952
‐ Cool, DM him,
and see what he says.

55
00:03:39,019 --> 00:03:40,521
While you're doing that,

56
00:03:40,587 --> 00:03:43,223
I'm gonna see how many creepers
I can get to creep on me.

57
00:03:43,289 --> 00:03:44,224
‐ Wait! You what?

58
00:03:44,290 --> 00:03:45,526
[yelps]

59
00:03:51,431 --> 00:03:54,568
‐ In case you're wondering,
43 dudes hit on me.

60
00:03:54,635 --> 00:03:57,504
I guess female avatars
are hard to come by here,

61
00:03:57,571 --> 00:04:00,340
which means I could set up
a reverse harem if I wanted.

62
00:04:00,406 --> 00:04:03,343
‐ [groans]
‐ Well? What'd your pal M say?

63
00:04:03,409 --> 00:04:05,245
Will he spot me some credits?

64
00:04:05,311 --> 00:04:07,413
‐ Yup. He said no problem.

65
00:04:11,718 --> 00:04:13,854
