66
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,355
‐ Awesome!

67
00:04:20,561 --> 00:04:23,363
Huh. Guess that's it.

68
00:04:25,165 --> 00:04:27,968
Convenient.
Password's preloaded.

69
00:04:28,034 --> 00:04:29,302
‐ Oh?

70
00:04:29,369 --> 00:04:31,104
‐ [coins clink]
‐ [fanfare plays]

71
00:04:31,171 --> 00:04:33,439
‐ [gasps]
‐ [laughs]

72
00:04:33,507 --> 00:04:36,242
Wait. That amount's
not a mistake, is it?

73
00:04:36,309 --> 00:04:38,478
‐ It's legit.
‐ He doesn't expect me

74
00:04:38,545 --> 00:04:39,846
to pay him back with a kidney

75
00:04:39,913 --> 00:04:42,048
or work this off
on a tuna boat, does he?!

76
00:04:42,115 --> 00:04:43,717
‐ I doubt it.

77
00:04:44,985 --> 00:04:45,952
‐ Hmm.

78
00:04:46,019 --> 00:04:48,622
Welp, whoever M is,
I'm marrying him.

79
00:04:48,689 --> 00:04:50,757
I need his info right now.

80
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:57,330
I'm super glad my strength and
stamina levels transferred over.

81
00:04:57,397 --> 00:04:59,600
I'll load up on gear I love.

82
00:04:59,666 --> 00:05:02,268
