and long lances!

83
00:05:02,335 --> 00:05:04,270
‐ This game doesn't have those!

84
00:05:04,337 --> 00:05:07,440
So? Do you see
anything you like?

85
00:05:07,508 --> 00:05:09,943
‐ Uh‐uh. I'm not feeling these.

86
00:05:10,010 --> 00:05:13,279
I was hoping to carry something
a little more medieval.

87
00:05:13,346 --> 00:05:14,915
‐ [thinking]
<i>If Pito or M were here,</i>

88
00:05:14,981 --> 00:05:18,284
they could point her
in the right direction. [gasps]

89
00:05:18,351 --> 00:05:21,622
I know a place that might
have what you're looking for!

90
00:05:21,688 --> 00:05:22,656
‐ Okay!

91
00:05:23,790 --> 00:05:24,891
LLENN!

92
00:05:24,958 --> 00:05:26,893
[gasping]

93
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:29,696
This gun is super cool.

94
00:05:29,763 --> 00:05:31,565
It's the prettiest,
most gorgeous,

95
00:05:31,632 --> 00:05:34,768
most beautiful gun
I've ever seen! [giggles]

96
00:05:35,636 --> 00:05:37,504
‐ That thing? Are you kidding?

97
00:05:37,571 --> 00:05:39,506
<i>It's fugly.</i>

98
00:05:39,573 --> 00:05:42,208
‐ That right there's
a brand‐spankin'‐new

99
00:05:42,275 --> 00:05:43,610
repeating grenade launcher.

100
00:05:43,677 --> 00:05:46,613
Heh! I got a pair of 'em in
just the other day.

101
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:49,182
‐ A grenade launcher? For real?

102
00:05:49,249 --> 00:05:51,818
‐ Yeah, you can shoot grenades
instead of throwing 'em.

103
00:05:51,885 --> 00:05:56,422
The ammo looks like an oversized
bullet filled with gunpowder.

104
00:05:56,489 --> 00:05:57,524
‐ Sounds dangerous.

105
00:05:57,591 --> 00:05:58,992
‐ If you like
long‐range weapons,

106
00:05:59,059 --> 00:06:00,861
that right there's
your honey bunny.

107
00:06:00,927 --> 00:06:03,396
It shoots grenades
up to 400 meters out.

108
00:06:03,463 --> 00:06:05,431
‐ Now you're talking!
It's not only cute,

109
00:06:05,498 --> 00:06:07,534
it's even radder
than a plain old gun!

110
00:06:07,601 --> 00:06:10,904
‐ When you aim, the Bullet Lines
are these cool parabolas!

111
00:06:10,971 --> 00:06:13,574
And since it's a revolver,
you can send six grenades

112
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,241
